00:17:33,527 --> 00:17:35,487
You can recover from
all injuries by Qiong Qi's.

269
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:37,440
But why do you have
so many scars?

270
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,047
Wars wait for no men.

271
00:17:39,112 --> 00:17:40,552
When do I have the time to heal?

272
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,831
So as time passes,

273
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,240
scars naturally stay.

274
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:44,800
But they are just external injuries.

275
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:46,120
It's nothing.

276
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:47,560
Don't you feel pain?

277
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:49,080
They've long recovered.

278
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:52,520
I guess being Supreme Immortal
is not easy too.

279
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,040
Obviously.

280
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,480
The Way of Heaven...

281
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:58,295
is paved with endless pain
but sparse healing.

282
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,487
Do everything...

283
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:00,880
in adequacy.

284
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:03,440
The higher the magical prowess,
the stronger one becomes.

285
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,720
The more responsibility and
bigger the mission one bears.

286
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,480
The more there are that...

287
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:08,720
one needs to protect.

288
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:13,320
I heard Chief Peony mention once,

289
00:18:13,351 --> 00:18:14,591
in the Floral Realm,

290
00:18:16,160 --> 00:18:19,200
if Ganoderma essence is applied,

291
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:21,520
those badly injured can heal,

292
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:23,120
normal people can get stronger...

293
00:18:23,320 --> 00:18:25,080
from ingesting it.

294
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:27,800
Seeing that Your Highness
has saved my life,

295
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:30,200
I'll give you one.

296
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:33,640
Ganoderma essence is rare
and sacred in the Floral Realm.

297
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:35,880
You need not bother
Chief Peony for my sake.

298
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:40,440
Mr. Hu said before,

299
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:42,320
people who look good,

300
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:44,640
spend all their effort in
caring for their face.

301
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:46,920
Therefore, their brains
are usually empty.

302
00:18:47,280 --> 00:18:48,760
You, are the perfect example.

303
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:51,400
You're the one who kidnapped me here.

304
00:18:51,760 --> 00:18:54,000
Why would Chief Peony save you?

305
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:55,440
If that's the case,

306
00:18:55,600 --> 00:18:57,000
how would you give it to me?

307
00:18:57,465 --> 00:18:58,585
It's just some grass.

308
00:18:58,720 --> 00:19:00,560
I'll just cast it out for you.

309
00:19:00,633 --> 00:19:01,753
You, cast it out?

310
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:05,000
Don't look down on me.

311
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:06,840
That's actually really easy.

312
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:09,647
You better think about
how you should thank me,

313
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,800
after I cast it out.

314
00:19:12,535 --> 00:19:13,607
All right,

315
00:19:13,816 --> 00:19:15,936
I'll be waiting then.

316
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:20,240
Just you wait.

317
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:23,120
Wait and see.

318
00:19:50,482 --> 00:19:52,722
If you can plant the Ganoderma,

319
00:19:52,953 --> 00:19:54,953
I'll give you 200 years worth
of magical prowess.

320
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,366
What say you?

321
00:19:56,545 --> 00:19:58,905
I know you're just teasing me.

322
00:19:59,345 --> 00:20:01,345
But us fruit planters,

323
00:20:01,449 --> 00:20:03,729
do not share the same thoughts
with the birds.

324
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:06,360
Three hundred years.

325
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,440
All right, 300 years then.

326
00:20:55,224 --> 00:20:56,624
I... I...

327
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:58,680
I... I've planted it!

328
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:00,280
I've grown the Ganoderma!

329
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:04,440
Look!

330
00:21:04,976 --> 00:21:06,478
Three hundred years
of magical prowess.

331
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,760
Losers pay the rake!

332
00:21:08,696 --> 00:21:10,176
What are you?

333
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,040
What's wrong?

334
00:21:13,232 --> 00:21:15,162
Ganoderma essence is a
sacred to the Floral Realm.

335
00:21:15,224 --> 00:21:17,704
How can a nobody like you
grow something like that?

336
00:21:17,859 --> 00:21:18,758
Let me ask you,

337
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,873
how are you related
to the late Floral Immortal?

338
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,920
The late Floral Immortal had
great magical prowess.

339
00:21:22,984 --> 00:21:24,442
High above all immortals.

340
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:26,440
If only I could be related to that.

341
00:21:27,248 --> 00:21:29,808
I'm not joking around, who are you?

342
00:21:29,888 --> 00:21:32,145
I'm just a grape,
what's wrong with you?

343
00:21:32,353 --> 00:21:34,278
Have you changed your mind
about the magical prowess?

344
00:21:34,280 --> 00:21:35,640
You can just say so.

345
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,149
Why are you being like this?

346
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,080
Fox fairy, why are you here?

347
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:19,440
<i>As the wind breezes by,</i>

348
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:26,160
<i>separating Heaven and Earth
to a million miles.</i>

349
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:29,919
<i>So, what?</i>

350
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,680
Moon Immortal was right,

351
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:34,440
to hold down a man,
is to first hold his kiss.

352
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,960
But why do I feel weird?

353
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,920
The rest is still usable.

354
00:22:44,407 --> 00:22:45,446
Keep it.

355
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,600
Don't waste my Ganoderma!

356
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:57,600
<i>Never to meet again in all eternity,</i>

357
00:22:57,760 --> 00:23:02,120
<i>despite how frantic the world becomes.</i>

358
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:09,400
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where we meet in every life.</i>

359
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:14,960
<i>There I'll wait for us to
watch the setting sun.</i>

360
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:21,560
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where we love in every life.</i>

361
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:27,400
<i>There I'll sing in the moonlight.</i>

362
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:33,520
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where I make a wish in every life.</i>

363
00:23:33,840 --> 00:23:39,040
<i>There I'll plant a red lotus to fill
the memories with its lovely scent.</i>

364
00:23:39,809 --> 00:23:42,049
<i>In a love letter, I found a place...</i>

365
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:43,135
Rou Rou.

366
00:23:43,784 --> 00:23:46,144
Phoenix got hurt because
he tried to save me.

367
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,039
Yet,

368
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:50,400
this cunning bird...

369
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,000
said he's fully recovered.

370
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:53,880
Who knows if he's really recovered?

371
00:23:54,800 --> 00:23:57,240
He even sacrificed his life for me.

372
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:58,920
If I left just like that,

373
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:00,640
it'd be too unfair...

374
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,240
right?

375
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:07,800
Even if not for him,

376
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:09,399
but for you,

377
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:12,320
I too, must go to Demon Realm
to find Qiong Qi.

378
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:13,880
To avenge you!

379
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:24,880
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where we meet in every life.</i>

380
00:24:24,912 --> 00:24:29,992
<i>There I'll wait for us to
watch the setting sun.</i>

381
00:24:30,824 --> 00:24:36,944
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where we love in every life.</i>

382
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:42,680
<i>There I'll sing in the moonlight.</i>

383
00:24:42,809 --> 00:24:48,649
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where I make a wish in every life.</i>

384
00:24:48,824 --> 00:24:54,424
<i>There I'll plant a red lotus to fill
the memories with its lovely scent.</i>

385
00:24:54,880 --> 00:25:00,240
<i>In a love letter, I found the place
where we love in every life.</i>

386
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:03,920
Congratulations, Your Highness.

387
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:05,640
What of?

388
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,720
I heard that Your Highness
caused great pain...

389
00:25:07,905 --> 00:25:09,145
to Qiong Qi with your powers.

390
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:11,198
The Heavenly Emperor personally gifted
the Red Clouds Sword...

391
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:13,051
which can kill immortals and
subdue demons.

392
00:25:13,168 --> 00:25:15,680
That sword is Heaven Realm's
greatest treasure.

393
00:25:15,921 --> 00:25:19,041
The Heavenly Emperor's action
of doing so speaks volumes.

394
00:25:19,225 --> 00:25:20,785
Your aunt is too, greatly thrilled.

395
00:25:21,153 --> 00:25:23,793
Therefore, I have come forth
especially to congratulate you.

396
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:27,080
It was only a duty,
there's nothing to be congratulated.

397
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:31,720
What is it that brings you here
so early in the day?

398
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,720
Your Highness,
you are journeying far.

399
00:25:33,841 --> 00:25:35,321
I came to send you off.

400
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:38,240
Also, I heard some rumours yesterday.

401
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:41,360
Saying that, Jin Mi is the person
Chief Peony is after.

402
00:25:41,593 --> 00:25:42,633
Is this true?

403
00:25:43,320 --> 00:25:44,960
You sure are well-informed.

404
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:48,640
Seems like Qiwu Palace
should do an in-house clean up.

405
00:25:49,456 --> 00:25:51,296
No wonder I couldn't
find a single soul...

406
00:25:51,569 --> 00:25:53,329
as I searched the entire bird tribe.

407
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:56,640
Jin Mi is really headstrong.

408
00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:58,040
Just by her alone,

409
00:25:58,120 --> 00:26:00,018
she caused so much trouble
to the bird tribe.

410
00:26:00,128 --> 00:26:01,408
You can't blame Jin Mi,

411
00:26:01,704 --> 00:26:04,424
it was I who took her here
to Heaven Realm.

412
00:26:04,665 --> 00:26:06,865
I'll apologize to Chief Peony.

413
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:08,653
To clear up the misunderstanding.

414
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:09,871
Surely.

415
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:12,182
So long as the Floral Realm and
the bird tribe are on good terms,

416
00:26:12,184 --> 00:26:13,493
I'll have a peace of mind.

417
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:17,400
Just that, I used to think
I knew Jin Mi.

418
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:20,240
Yet she even hid her identity from me.

419
00:26:20,433 --> 00:26:21,763
I'm just so disappointed.

420
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:23,277
You've always been benevolent.

421
00:26:23,407 --> 00:26:26,167
Don't compare yourself to Jin Mi,
that clutter-brain.

422
00:26:50,577 --> 00:26:52,051
Phoenix has great powers.

423
00:26:52,176 --> 00:26:54,076
Hopefully he doesn't figure it out.

424
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:14,790
Ouch.

425
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,848
Your Highness,

426
00:27:17,080 --> 00:27:19,320
this shirt has got some dirt on it.

427
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,601
Your Highness,

428
00:27:20,766 --> 00:27:22,597
it might be because
this scroll is aged.

429
00:27:22,624 --> 00:27:24,584
It's not properly dusted,
thus dusting the shirt.

430
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:27,631
Your Highness, shall I get a
change of clothes for you?

431
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:31,560
Your Highness,
how about this purple one?

432
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:33,200
It's a little too bright.

433
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:36,120
Then, Your Highness,
what about the black one?

434
00:27:36,232 --> 00:27:37,432
That's too gloomy.

435
00:27:39,416 --> 00:27:40,589
No worries.

436
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:42,240
A little dust is fine.

437
00:27:42,520 --> 00:27:43,798
I'll just wear this.

438
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,800
That's right.

439
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:48,391
Ouch!

440
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:50,869
It hurts!

441
00:27:55,002 --> 00:27:58,288
"Bank of Wangchuan River"

442
00:28:17,441 --> 00:28:19,681
Young man, are you looking for a ride?

443
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:20,920
Exactly.

444
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,356
Sorry to trouble you, sir.

445
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,472
Please.

446
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,680
Please stand firm, young man.

447
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:32,400
The fairy in the sleeve pocket too,
hold on tight.

448
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:36,080
I'm going to take off.

449
00:28:36,289 --> 00:28:39,289
Fairy in sleeve pocket, hold on tight.

450
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:45,840
That...

451
00:28:52,320 --> 00:28:55,120
I don't know how but I slept
in the wrong place, last night.

452
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:57,320
How unfortunate.
How unfortunate indeed.

453
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,479
This is Wangchuan River.

454
00:29:12,080 --> 00:29:15,280
If you don't wish to be the food of
the souls in the river, sit still.

455
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:24,000
Where's your grape vines?

456
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,978
I worried that wearing it
would wound your pride,

457
00:29:25,980 --> 00:29:27,020
so I kept it.

458
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:30,706
Why would my pride be wounded?

459
00:29:31,239 --> 00:29:32,678
Obviously because I worry,
I'd snatch away...

460
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,734
your reputation as the most
handsome man in the six realms.

461
00:29:34,736 --> 00:29:36,489
My whole 10,000 years of watching...

462
00:29:36,520 --> 00:29:39,047
River of Unmindfulness,
this is my second time...

463
00:29:39,120 --> 00:29:41,080
seeing such a stunning lady.

464
00:29:42,313 --> 00:29:44,233
Isn't your business
doing too bad then.

465
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:47,065
Only 2 ladies in 10,000 years.

466
00:29:47,419 --> 00:29:49,339
I still remember,
about 10,000 years ago...

467
00:29:49,472 --> 00:29:50,912
there once was a lady...

468
00:29:51,304 --> 00:29:53,504
who came to me for
a handful of water from this river.

469
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:56,113
That lady had the skin of a goddess.

470
00:29:56,257 --> 00:29:58,497
She walked like she was
on a field of flowers.

471
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,040
Her feature's stunning.

472
00:30:00,208 --> 00:30:01,728
But she looked miserable.

473
00:30:01,904 --> 00:30:04,904
Unlike this lady here,
who's bright and naive.

474
00:30:05,169 --> 00:30:07,490
Sounds like an interesting story.

475
00:30:07,817 --> 00:30:09,857
I'll tell this to the Moon Immortal
when I get back.

476
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,478
He'd definitely be delighted.

477
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:13,711
Then what happened?
What happened next?

478
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:16,236
Then from the shore,
came a man with brocade clothing.

479
00:30:16,353 --> 00:30:19,226
Hurriedly he spilled the water
from the hands of the lady.

480
00:30:19,496 --> 00:30:21,100
After a struggle between the two.

481
00:30:21,249 --> 00:30:23,665
The girl leaped up,
seeming to dive into the river.

482
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,520
Then the man panicked.

483
00:30:25,608 --> 00:30:27,648
As if he'd gone mad,
and tried to pull her back.

484
00:30:28,474 --> 00:30:31,715
In the end,
the two of them disappeared...

485
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:33,240
and was nowhere to be seen.

486
00:30:34,561 --> 00:30:36,561
River of Unmindfulness.

487
00:30:36,721 --> 00:30:40,785
Looking back, it's all
become a distant memory.

488
00:30:41,120 --> 00:30:44,200
So it's a story with a bad finish.

489
00:31:14,698 --> 00:31:15,920
Stand firm.

490
00:31:20,306 --> 00:31:21,666
Told you to be careful.

491
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:22,880
You clumsy mess.

492
00:31:26,928 --> 00:31:28,848
What a moody birdy.

493
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:34,732
Don't leave me here alone.

494
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:36,800
I'll be scared all alone here.

495
00:31:37,857 --> 00:31:38,977
You're a elfin.

496
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,592
What could possibly scare you?

497
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:42,126
Oh yeah.

498
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:43,397
You've got a point.

499
00:31:44,130 --> 00:31:45,850
What? I'm no elfin.

500
00:31:46,056 --> 00:31:47,376
I'm a fairy.

501
00:31:47,560 --> 00:31:48,608
From today on,

502
00:31:48,768 --> 00:31:51,327
you will be my personal maid
in the Demon Realm.

503
00:31:51,425 --> 00:31:52,524
Assist me closely.

504
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:55,960
And I'll make sure you don't get
captured by demons. How's that?

505
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:59,360
All right.

506
00:32:06,753 --> 00:32:08,393
Why did you make
my hair into 2 pigtails?

507
00:32:08,464 --> 00:32:10,104
This is so old-fashioned!

508
00:32:10,584 --> 00:32:12,544
Why did you make
my hair into 2 pigtails?

509
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,367
I hate pigtails.

510
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:15,560
I think it looks great.

511
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:17,120
Two pigtails don't look good at all!

512
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:19,080
I think it looks great.

513
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,843
Mr. Demon,
come buy this tail.

514
00:32:21,912 --> 00:32:22,992
I have only the freshest.

515
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:25,400
Once you put it on,
I assure you will be in disguise.

516
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:28,160
How real!

517
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:29,689
It's still warm.

518
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:34,120
Do you have bunny ears?

519
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:35,560
I do, I do, I do!

520
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,520
Wow, really?

521
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:41,280
Now I can go back and
give Mr. Hu a scare.

522
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:43,854
Do I look cute?
Cute, aren't I?

523
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:45,160
You have such great taste.

524
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:47,000
This rabbit ears are made
according to...

525
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:49,560
- the Jade Rabbit of Guanghan Palace.
- Really?

526
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:51,160
Don't get tricked.

527
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:55,040
All right!

528
00:32:55,681 --> 00:32:56,681
Ms. Demon,

529
00:32:56,745 --> 00:32:58,385
you have not given me
any magical prowess.

530
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,605
What magical prowess?

531
