532
00:33:04,089 --> 00:33:05,252
Fish Fairy?

533
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,200
Fairy Jin Mi.

534
00:33:06,272 --> 00:33:08,352
- Why are you here?
- You seem well.

535
00:33:09,979 --> 00:33:12,419
- Thanks Fish Fairy.
- Cute, right? You like it?

536
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,840
This.

537
00:33:18,424 --> 00:33:19,704
It's my maid who is buying,

538
00:33:19,813 --> 00:33:21,192
