539
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:23,320
How could I trouble
The Night Immortal.

540
00:33:23,368 --> 00:33:26,208
It's no trouble between brothers.

541
00:33:26,992 --> 00:33:28,232
Brothers?

542
00:33:28,432 --> 00:33:29,792
You are brothers?

543
00:33:30,089 --> 00:33:31,689
The Heaven Realm is truly weird.

544
00:33:32,233 --> 00:33:34,833
First there was the Fox uncle.

545
00:33:35,082 --> 00:33:37,162
Now there's a handsome fish brother.

546
00:33:38,986 --> 00:33:42,026
Everyone is connected in this world.

547
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:44,280
Looks like you know each other.

548
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:46,238
That day, Fish Fairy was
feeding the deer in Heaven,

549
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,520
and I ran into him.

550
00:33:47,761 --> 00:33:48,860
Fish?

551
00:33:50,512 --> 00:33:51,752
The Night Immortal,

552
00:33:51,872 --> 00:33:53,592
when did you decide to
forgo being a dragon,

553
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:55,050
but become a fish instead?

554
00:33:55,135 --> 00:33:56,335
The Night Immortal?

555
00:33:57,425 --> 00:33:59,785
I heard that a while back...

556
00:33:59,848 --> 00:34:01,888
The Fire Immortal became a crow
back in the Floral Realm.

557
00:34:01,966 --> 00:34:04,606
Me becoming a fish
is nothing compared to that.

558
00:34:05,241 --> 00:34:06,247
You.

559
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:09,626
You're the Night Dragon, the Night Immortal?

560
00:34:09,801 --> 00:34:12,241
I guess having a tail with scales,
doesn't mean you're a fish.

561
00:34:12,271 --> 00:34:14,348
You could be
a low-profile dragon too.

562
00:34:14,535 --> 00:34:16,575
It never occurred to me,
that Jin Mi, you...

563
00:34:16,728 --> 00:34:18,288
are the Fire Immortal's maidservant.

564
00:34:18,505 --> 00:34:20,102
How very interesting.

565
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:24,216
What brings the Night Immortal
to the Demon Realm?

566
00:34:24,417 --> 00:34:26,417
You coming here personally
to capture Qiong Qi...

567
00:34:26,600 --> 00:34:27,679
has made me worry.

568
00:34:27,792 --> 00:34:29,112
So I came to lend a helping hand.

569
00:34:29,473 --> 00:34:30,873
Qiong Qi is truly ferocious.

570
00:34:31,161 --> 00:34:33,295
I may not be able to protect you.

571
00:34:33,480 --> 00:34:34,520
Rest assured.

572
00:34:34,608 --> 00:34:35,968
I won't drag you down.

573
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,600
- Let's go then.
- Let's.

574
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,400
What a big room!

575
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,014
Where... where should I sleep?

576
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:58,303
You're my personal maid.

577
00:34:58,320 --> 00:35:00,036
Of course you have to serve me.

578
00:35:02,242 --> 00:35:03,442
That doesn't seem very good.

579
00:35:03,482 --> 00:35:05,802
I'm not used to sharing a bed.

580
00:35:06,200 --> 00:35:07,360
This is a suite.

581
00:35:07,419 --> 00:35:08,920
Of course you'll have your own bed.

582
00:35:09,048 --> 00:35:10,798
Tonight, I'll be discussing the
battle plan with his highness.

583
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,118
You go prepare some
fine wine and food...

584
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:13,480
and send it to my room.

585
00:35:46,442 --> 00:35:48,362
He knows just how to make me busy.

586
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:10,160
Why are you here in Demon Realm too?

587
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:19,160
Mr. Hu...

588
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:21,120
The past year...

589
00:36:21,560 --> 00:36:25,000
has been a great memory.

590
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:30,920
Immortal,
you have a letter.

591
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:38,280
Immortal.

592
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:40,160
This was written by Jin Mi to you.

593
00:36:41,631 --> 00:36:42,706
Jin Mi?

594
00:36:56,240 --> 00:37:00,440
Little one!

595
00:37:06,480 --> 00:37:07,520
Little deer,

596
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:08,600
morning.

597
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:13,128
Here.

598
00:37:13,457 --> 00:37:14,977
Have a bit of grass.

599
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:18,176
This grass
is hard to find in this Demon Realm.

600
00:37:18,321 --> 00:37:19,918
Don't just feed on dreams,

601
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:21,084
have some greens too.

602
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:22,360
Then, you'll be healthier.

603
00:37:22,640 --> 00:37:24,480
Have some grass.
Grass.

604
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:26,320
Come on, come get it.

605
00:37:26,824 --> 00:37:28,009
Here you go.

606
00:37:28,297 --> 00:37:30,297
Jin Mi, don't force it.

607
00:37:31,737 --> 00:37:32,977
Fish Fairy.

608
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:36,062
Jin Mi, you may not know...

609
00:37:36,225 --> 00:37:38,185
but the Beast of Dreams
only feeds on dreams.

610
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,360
So, it can't eat grass.

611
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:41,551
Let it out at night,

612
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:42,935
and it'll go hunting for dreams.

613
00:37:42,998 --> 00:37:43,998
Then it'll eat.

614
00:37:44,120 --> 00:37:45,520
Only eats dreams?

615
00:37:46,425 --> 00:37:48,105
I wonder if the dreams taste any good.

616
00:37:48,344 --> 00:37:50,184
Is it sweet? Salty?

617
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,520
This Little one,

618
00:38:41,704 --> 00:38:42,847
hit a jackpot and had...

619
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:44,200
pretty girls in his dreams.

620
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,456
But this dream...

621
00:38:45,536 --> 00:38:47,336
why did it change at the end?

622
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:49,600
There are 2 types of dreams.

623
00:38:49,720 --> 00:38:51,160
One is a blue dream from memory.

624
00:38:51,345 --> 00:38:52,905
The other is a yellow dream of desire.

625
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:56,948
When people dream
of the things that had once happened,

626
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:59,603
then, the dream beads
will glow with a blue light.

627
00:38:59,680 --> 00:39:01,419
Which is the blue coloured
dream of memory.

628
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:03,600
If it's a dream that has
never really happened,

629
00:39:03,680 --> 00:39:04,870
but just imagination.

630
00:39:04,992 --> 00:39:07,720
Then the dream bead
will let out a yellow glow.

631
00:39:07,832 --> 00:39:09,632
Which is the yellow coloured
dream of desire.

632
00:39:09,712 --> 00:39:12,512
People often dream
of reality at the very beginning...

633
00:39:12,617 --> 00:39:13,897
of their dream.

634
00:39:14,255 --> 00:39:15,272
But then...

635
00:39:15,384 --> 00:39:17,024
it gradually fills with...

636
00:39:17,099 --> 00:39:18,400
all sorts of imagination.

637
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,720
This dream will change from
a blue dream of memory...

638
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:22,720
to a yellow dream of desire.

639
00:39:24,505 --> 00:39:25,665
It sounds super complex.

640
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,120
To put it simply,

641
00:39:27,408 --> 00:39:29,359
can I say, that a
yellow dream is fake...

642
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,726
and a blue dream is real?

643
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,040
If it's both blue and yellow,

644
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:33,497
then it's half fake and half real.

645
00:39:33,880 --> 00:39:34,912
That's right.

646
00:39:35,008 --> 00:39:36,368
Jin Mi, you are correct.

647
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,880
Oh yes, breakfast is served.

648
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:39,993
Let's go eat.

649
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:42,760
Don't worry about me, you go ahead.
I'll be there in a bit.

650
00:39:42,775 --> 00:39:44,735
All right, I'll be going first.

651
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:49,560
Little Beast of Dreams.

652
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:51,640
The dream you just spit out
was really meaningful.

653
00:39:51,696 --> 00:39:52,896
Give me another, won't you?

654
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:08,000
Isn't that Phoenix?

655
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:12,760
This must be the erotic dream that...

656
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:14,240
Moon Immortal mentioned.

657
00:40:14,712 --> 00:40:15,992
Fancy that!,

658
00:40:16,305 --> 00:40:17,625
The rascal, Phoenix.

659
00:40:17,921 --> 00:40:19,601
He always looks so serious.

660
00:40:19,928 --> 00:40:21,808
Yet he has such erotic dream.

661
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:38,240
This girl...

662
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:40,240
Why does she look exactly like me?

663
00:40:44,488 --> 00:40:45,488
Tell me,

664
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:47,640
who's that woman
hugging the Fire Immortal?

665
00:40:47,857 --> 00:40:49,972
Isn't this woman
the Demon Realm general?

666
00:40:51,456 --> 00:40:52,675
I have no idea too.

667
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:53,977
I was just looking too.

668
00:40:54,056 --> 00:40:55,320
With that whip of yours,

669
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,920
I couldn't see anything.

670
00:40:58,208 --> 00:40:59,368
And who are you?

671
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:02,129
How dare you spy on the dreams
of the Supreme Immortal?

672
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:03,296
Me?

673
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:06,000
I am his highness
The Fire Immortal's maidservant.

674
00:41:06,788 --> 00:41:08,742
The Fire Immortal,
where is he?

675
00:41:10,112 --> 00:41:11,471
Come, come, I'll tell you.

676
00:41:11,560 --> 00:41:12,655
He's eating right now.

677
00:41:12,765 --> 00:41:14,854
Just go straight, turn left,
left and left again.

678
00:41:14,936 --> 00:41:17,056
When you get there,
turn right and you'll see him.

679
00:41:17,152 --> 00:41:18,232
Go on!

680
00:41:19,633 --> 00:41:21,593
I got to find a good spot
to watch it unfold.

681
00:41:22,508 --> 00:41:24,114
The food in Heaven Realm are bland,

682
00:41:24,160 --> 00:41:26,400
After a long time, it feels dull.

683
00:41:26,649 --> 00:41:28,929
Eating spicy and sweet food
once in a while...

684
00:41:29,025 --> 00:41:30,225
is quite a pleasure.

685
00:41:31,120 --> 00:41:34,040
Coming out from the Second Prince
who eats only fruits of bamboo,

686
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,726
only drinks from the purest spring,

687
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,960
that's rather interesting.

688
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:41,254
Cheers,

689
00:41:44,680 --> 00:41:45,880
Fairy Jin Mi.

690
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,587
No one came to see you yet?
